Tribe KRD is a web-based application which can be used by administrative personel of educational organizations (like schools). It provides functionality to register new students, follow the scholar careers of these students, grade these students and transfer the relevant data to the Dutch national educational platform (named 'BRON') in order to fullfill all legal obligations.
Tribe KRD is a fully webbased, multi-tenant, Software-as-a-service solution.

For more info visit https://joinup.ec.europa.eu/software/tribe-krd/description
